  "sketchCode": "// Example: Stepper Motor (28BYJ-48 + ULN2003)\n// Rotate the shaft one full revolution each way with the Stepper library.\n\n#include <Stepper.h>\n\nconst int stepsPerRev = 2048;\n// 28BYJ-48 coil order for Stepper.h is IN1, IN3, IN2, IN4.\nStepper stepper(stepsPerRev, 8, 10, 9, 11);\n\nvoid setup() {\n  stepper.setSpeed(12); // rpm\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  stepper.step(stepsPerRev);   // one revolution clockwise\n  delay(500);\n  stepper.step(-stepsPerRev);  // one revolution counter-clockwise\n  delay(500);\n}\n",
